name: Spiritum Portals - Balance
description: White Sands National Monument. A mystical beach - the remnants of an ancient sea amidst the mountains, used as a nuclear missile test range -- surely the lore of White Sands is a peek into the history they would have us believe. Let the crystally whites, the lone cacti, the hazy sandstorms, and the purple dusk of White Sands be a portal into the your own reality.
